===Examples===
;Example 1a
: '''Status Resistance Bonus and Status Resistance Multiplier'''
: {{H|Spirit Breaker}} has {{I|Sange and Yasha}} equipped with level 2 {{A|Spirit Breaker|Bulldoze}} active. What is his current status resistance? 

:: Base unit status resistance: {{G|status resistance}}
:: Bonus status resistance: {{A|Spirit Breaker|Bulldoze}} {{#expr:{{#vardefineecho:bulldoze sr|({{#explode:{{#explode:{{Show|A|Spirit Breaker|Bulldoze|value2}}|/|1}}|%}}/100)}}}}, {{I|Sange and Yasha}} {{#expr:{{#vardefineecho:sny sr|({{Show|I|Sange and Yasha|bonus status resistance}}/100)}}}}

:: Total Status Resistance
:: = {{#vardefineecho:sb1a|1 - (1 - {{G|status resistance}}) * (1 - {{#expr:{{#var:bulldoze sr}}}}) * (1 - {{#expr:{{#var:sny sr}}}})}}
:: = {{#expr:{{#var:sb1a}}}}

: {{H|Spirit Breaker}} currently has {{#expr:({{#var:sb1a}})*100}}% status resistance in this example, and all debuff duration applied on him will now be multiplied by {{#expr:1-({{#var:sb1a}})}}.

;Example 1b
: '''Debuff Duration and Status Resistance Multiplier'''
: How long would a {{#vardefineecho:db value|3}}-second {{M|debuff}} duration be on {{H|Spirit Breaker}} from the previous example?

:: Total Debuff Duration
:: = {{#var:db value}} * {{#expr:1-({{#var:sb1a}})}}
:: = {{#vardefineecho:sb1b|{{#expr:{{#var:db value}}*(1-({{#var:sb1a}})) round2}}}}

: The {{M|debuff}} duration will affect {{H|Spirit Breaker}} for a duration of {{#var:sb1b}}s instead of {{#var:db value}}s in this example.

;Example 2
: '''Calculating Actual or Total Debuff Duration'''
: {{H|Spirit Breaker}} from the previous example now has both {{I|Sange and Yasha}}. 
: He is currently affected by a 0.1-status resistance reduction.
: The enemy {{H|Rubick}} now has {{I|Timeless Relic}} equipped. How long would a {{#var:db value}}-second {{M|debuff}} duration be on {{H|Spirit Breaker}} now?

:: Base unit status resistance: {{G|status resistance}}
:: Bonus status resistance: {{I|Sange and Yasha}} {{#var:sny sr}}
:: Status resistance reduction: {{#vardefineecho:reduce sr|-0.1}}

:: Total Status Resistance:
:: = 1 - (1 - {{G|status resistance}}) * (1 - {{#expr:{{#var:sny sr}}}}) * (1 -  <span style="font-weight:bold; color:crimson;">{{#var:reduce sr}}</span>)
:: = {{#expr:{{#vardefineecho:sb2|1 - (1 - {{G|status resistance}}) * (1 - ({{#var:sny sr}})) * (1 - ({{#var:reduce sr}}))}}}}

: {{H|Spirit Breaker}} currently has {{#expr:({{#var:sb2}})*100}}% status resistance in this example, and all debuff duration applied on him will now be multiplied by {{#expr:1-({{#var:sb2}})}}, before other debuff duration amplification applied.
<!--
:: Debuff duration amplification: {{I|Timeless Relic}} {{#vardefineecho:trelic|{{#expr:{{#explode:{{Show|I|Timeless Relic|bonus debuff duration}}|%}}/100}}}}

:: Total Debuff Duration
:: = {{#var:rubicklift}} * {{#expr:1-({{#var:sb2}})}} * (1 - <span style="font-weight:bold; color:crimson;">-{{#var:trelic}}</span>)
:: = {{#vardefineecho:sb2|{{#expr:{{#var:rubicklift}}*(1-({{#var:sb2}}))*(1+{{#var:trelic}}) round2}}}}

: The level 4 {{A|Rubick|Telekinesis}} will affect {{H|Spirit Breaker}} for a duration of {{#var:sb2}}s instead of {{#var:rubicklift}}s in this example.-->

